dcterms:description: The training set consists of 199 clinical notes, and the development set has 99 notes, both collected from four types of clinical notes including discharge summaries, radiology reports, and ECG/ECHO reports. Disorder entities were annotated and mapped to UMLS CUIs of SNOMED-CT concepts.
